snippet.title: Deposition in Domestic Violence Injunction cases
snippet.description:
Depositions in domestic violence injunction cases? I do depositions in most of my injunction cases. Here is why. 

“We are your best friends at your worst times!”

I am Patrick McGeehan, and I am a family law and criminal defense lawyer in Miami, Florida. I receive a lot of questions regarding family law and domestic violence issues. In this video, I answer, Is everything I tell my lawyer confidential in Miami and Miami-Dade County, Florida?

We represent clients in Miami-Dade, Broward, Palm Beach, and Monroe Counties.  

Please feel free to contact our office to discuss your case:
